<title>SOUTH AFRICA: ERPM says in talks, cautions holders.</title>
<headline>ERPM says in talks, cautions holders.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>East Rand Proprietary Mines Ltd said on Friday talks were in progress which could impact on its share price.</p>
<p>Shareholders were advised to exercise caution in their share dealings until a further notice.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27 11 482 1003</p>
